::DarkMouse::

As she walked along she thought about all that had happened.  Why would this 
bot(Quickstrike) who cared nothing for her, hated her even, would risk his 
life for her.  WHy the hell did she kiss his cheek like that? she thought.  
She made a face at remembering that horrable mistake.
She knew that the other bot Scorponok hated her as well.  She suddenly felt 
alone.  She thought that if they hated her so, would they help her out if 
she got into trouble?  Maybe not, she thought.  She wondered if she even had 
an ally in the Predacon camp.  She shook her head knowing that she didn't.  
she knew her orders and was going to carry them out as best as she could.  
But she knew that if she found trouble, she was as good as slagged.  No one 
would help her.  She was a tough little bot.  But she knew that in this 
large group of Predacons, she was alone.

She spotted a glittering object off in the distance.  She pointed at it.

"See that Scorponok?  Let's go over there and check it out."
